text: Uygar Mert Zeybek (born 4 June 1995) is a Turkish footballer who plays as a midfielder for İstanbulspor. == Club career == Zeybek is a youth exponent from Fenerbahçe. He made his Süper Lig debut at 31 May 2015 against Kasımpaşa.
